    <h1 class="w3-center">ONE KEY TO RHYTHM</h1>
    <p class="w3-center">
      There is one key to staying in rhythm: THE KICK DRUM IS YOUR METRONOME
    </p>
    <hr />
    <p>
      In house, each bar is music is divided into <span class="w3-tag w3-green">4 beats</span> in what's called <span class="w3-tag w3-green">4 on the Floor</span> beat that looks like this on a drum sequencer:
    </p>
    <div class="w3-margin-bottom w3-margin-top w3-center">
      <span class="w3-opacity w3-tag w3-white w3-text-white w3-large">BEAT</span>
      <span class="w3-opacity w3-tag w3-white w3-text-white w3-large">kick</span>
      <span class="w3-opacity w3-tag w3-amber w3-text-white w3-large">hihat</span>
      <span class="w3-opacity w3-tag w3-white w3-text-white w3-large">clap</span>
