      <span class="w3-opacity w3-tag w3-amber w3-text-white w3-large">hihat</span>
    </div>
    <div class="w3-margin-bottom w3-center">
      <span class="w3-opacity w3-tag w3-white w3-text-white w3-large">BEAT</span>
      <span class="w3-opacity w3-tag w3-white w3-text-white w3-large">kick</span>
      <span class="w3-opacity w3-tag w3-white w3-text-white w3-large">hihat</span>
      <span class="w3-opacity w3-tag w3-blue w3-large">clap</span>
      <span class="w3-opacity w3-tag w3-white w3-text-white w3-large">hihat</span>
      <span class="w3-opacity w3-tag w3-white w3-text-white w3-large">kick</span>
      <span class="w3-opacity w3-tag w3-white w3-text-white w3-large">hihat</span>
      <span class="w3-opacity w3-tag w3-blue w3-large">clap</span>
      <span class="w3-opacity w3-tag w3-white w3-text-white w3-large">hihat</span>
    </div>
    <div class="w3-margin-bottom w3-center">
      <span class="w3-opacity w3-tag w3-white w3-text-white w3-large">BEAT</span>
      <span class="w3-opacity w3-tag w3-red w3-large">kick</span>
      <span class="w3-opacity w3-tag w3-white w3-text-white w3-large">hihat</span>
      <span class="w3-opacity w3-tag w3-red w3-large">kick</span>
      <span class="w3-opacity w3-tag w3-white w3-text-white w3-large">hihat</span>
      <span class="w3-opacity w3-tag w3-red w3-large">kick</span>
      <span class="w3-opacity w3-tag w3-white w3-text-white w3-large">hihat</span>
      <span class="w3-opacity w3-tag w3-red w3-large">kick</span>
      <span class="w3-opacity w3-tag w3-white w3-text-white w3-large">hihat</span>
    </div>
    <p>
      Just as a metronome ticks back and forth to help you play piano in tempo, the kick is what are actually dancing to in music to stay in rhythm.
    </p>
    <p>
      Single out the kick drum every time you listen to music and eventually you will not be able to not hear it.
    </p>
    <p>
      Simply focus on getting from one count/beat/kick to the next (i.e., ignore half-counts/hihats) and you will learn far more intuitively, and your body will NATURALLY fill in the blanks!
    </p>

